## 2. Visualization tier (3 level)

### Tier 1: static markdown table (현재)
- 5-axis × 5-platform = 25 cells (knowledge_graph §1)
- 5-axis × 4-disease = 20 cells (§2)
- 5-platform × 4-disease = 20 cells (§3)
- 5-axis × Top 10 = 50 cells (§4)
- 5-platform × Top 10 = 50 cells (§5)
- Top 10 × 4-disease = 40 cells (§6)

**한계**: text-only, sortable 안 됨, 200-disease dimension 추가 시 explosive.

### Tier 2: interactive heatmap (proposed)
- **Plotly heatmap** — 5 dimension × 200 disease × 6 tier = 6000 cell heatmap
- **D3.js network graph** — node = manifest/disease/platform/paradigm, edge = cross-link (~30 nodes + ~150 edges)
- **Sankey diagram** — axis flow: 5-axis → 5-platform → 4-disease → Top 10 paradigm

### Tier 3: full Streamlit / Dash dashboard (target)
- **panel 1**: 5-axis radar chart (current adoption + Tier projection)
- **panel 2**: 200-disease heatmap (axis × platform × paradigm fit)
- **panel 3**: paradigm Top 10 timeline (Tier 0-5 progression)
- **panel 4**: 한국 K-platform 5사 × axis fit radar
- **panel 5**: ethics dimension × Top 10 score (bioethics_framework)
- **panel 6**: quantum HW adoption + AI/ML adoption parallel timeline
- **panel 7**: monthly review cron progress tracker
- **panel 8**: clinical translation pathway funnel (stage 0 → 12)

## 3. Dashboard tech stack proposal

| Component | Tech | 이유 |
|---|---|---|
| backend | Python 3.12+ | hexa-bio 의 existing pyphi.log + Aer simulator 환경 |
| dashboard framework | Streamlit (1차) → Dash (2차) | Streamlit = rapid prototype / Dash = production |
| visualization | Plotly + D3.js + matplotlib | interactive |
| data store | sqlite (1차) → Neo4j (2차) | sqlite = simple / Neo4j = graph relationship |
| LLM agent integration | Anthropic Claude API + OpenAI GPT-4 | dashboard 의 review prompt 자동 생성 |
| deployment | local (1차) → Streamlit Cloud / Hugging Face Spaces (2차) | free tier |
| Korean localization | i18next (한글/English toggle) | 사용자 한글 응답 선호 |

